 where the horror is. Watch a video of the author discussing the topic Haunted Homes (https://youtu.be/_irTEfvtZfQ).  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 01. Dez 2022) 0aHaunted houses in motion pictures. 0aSuburban life in motion pictures. 0aSuburban lifezUnited States. 0aSuburbs in motion pictures. 7aPERFORMING ARTS / General.2bisacsh  ahorror film, horror, television, Hollywood, Hereditary, The Haunting of Hill House, The Old Dark House, The Witch, The Babadook, haunted houses, suburbia, American suburbia, gothic, classic film, family dynamic, gender, race, economic collapse, family anxiety, film set, iconic houses, famous homes.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Arts 2021z9783110753790oZDB-23-DPK08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Arts, Architecture and Design 2021 Englishz978311075403208iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2021 Englishz978311075400108iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2021z9783110753776oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertRutgers University Press Complete eBook-Package 2021z978311073913840uhttps://doi.org/10.36019/978197880777840uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781978807778423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781978807778/original  a978-3-11-073913-8  Rutgers University Press Complete eBook-Package 2021b2021  a978-3-11-075400-1  EBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2021 Englishb2021  a978-3-11-075403-2  EBOOK PACKAGE Arts, Architecture and Design 2021 Englishb2021  aEBA_CL_MUAR  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_ECL_MUAR  aEBA_EEBKALL  aEBA_ESSHALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA13ENGE  aPDA17SSHEE  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DGGb2021  aZDB-23-DPKb2021